articles.title: A four-room flat was just sold for $1.25 million
articles.content: A four-room flat in Bishan was just sold for a record-high of $1.25 million. (Photo: Albert Chua/EdgeProp Singapore). The recent sale surpasses the previous high for four-room flats in Bishan. This flat has a shorter remaining lease of around 63 years. So far this year, 162 four-room flats in Bishan have been sold.
